PROGRAM-1-WRITE A GRADE CLASSIFIER : INPUT MARKS , OUTPUT A/B/C/D/F
CODE-
#Takes marks as input
marks = float(input("Enter your marks(0-100): "))
if marks >= 90:
    grade = "A"
elif marks >= 80:
    grade = "B"
elif marks >= 70:
    grade = "C"
elif marks >= 50:
    grade = "D"
else:
    grade = "F"
print("Grade:", grade)            #Display grade
OUTPUT-
Enter your marks(0-100): 76
Grade: C


