Found the secret number!


PROGRAM-6-PYRAMID STAR PATTERN USING NESTED LOOPS
code-
rows = int(input("Enter the number of rows: "))
for i in range(1, rows + 1):
    for j in range(rows - i):
        print(" ", end="")
    for k in range(2 * i - 1):
        print("*", end="")
    print()
